{"title":"POC Kortal Race MIPS mountain bike helmet goes high-tech, adds huge Devour sunglasses","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/02/pocs-new-high-tech-kortal-race-mips-helmet-and-devour-sunglasses/","date":1614693609000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Once a helmet is strong enough to pass certification, you might be satisfied thinking it’s as safe as it needs to be, but POC’s new Kortal Race MIPS could easily convince you otherwise. In addition to exceeding normal MTB safety standards, the Kortal Race MIPS carries several more high-tech features that could be very helpful in an emergency.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet and Devour sunglasses\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\" ezoid=\"0.231894806244487\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Devour-sunglasses-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\"></a></p><p>Alongside the Kortal helmet POC has also released their new Devour Clarity sunglasses. Featuring massive Clarity lenses, the Devours are intended to offer goggle-like coverage with less bulk and better ventilation. While they’ve been shaped to fit seamlessly with the Kortal helmet, the Devour sunglasses are intended for any type of cycling.</p><p>And you’ve already seen us wearing them with the new lightweight <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/23/review-poc-ultralight-ventral-lite-road-bike-helmet-is-their-lightest-ever-as-light-as-180g/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">POC Ventral Lite</a> road helmet, too….</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet, angle\" width=\"800\" height=\"673\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-297x250.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-768x646.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-696x586.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-499x420.jpg 499w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-297x250.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-768x646.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-696x586.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-orange-499x420.jpg 499w\"></a></p><p>Inspired by POC’s Tectal helmet, the Kortal Race MIPS is an all-new design that bears an edgier appearance along with new construction and even more safety features. There are two models of the new helmet: The Kortal Race MIPS is the fully-featured version and the Kortal is a base model that doesn’t include a MIPS system or any of those high-tech safety gadgets.</p><h3>MIPS Integra inside</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet, MIPS integra system\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-Integra-system-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The Kortal Race MIPS uses the all-new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/02/mips-integra-teases-more-integrated-helmet-protection-renames-air-evolve-essential/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MIPS Integra tech</a> that we gave a sneak peek at a month ago, neatly hiding the MIPS system within the helmet’s shell. The 360° adjustment system’s rear dial can be set to three different height positions.</p><h3>Recco &amp; NFC inside</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet, RECCO reflector and NFC ID chip\" width=\"800\" height=\"502\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-768x482.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-696x437.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-669x420.jpg 669w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-768x482.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-696x437.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-safety-devices-669x420.jpg 669w\"></a></p><p>There are two nifty technical features found in the Kortal Race MIPS: The first is an integrated RECCO reflector, which helps search and rescue teams using RECCO search devices to locate you in an emergency. &nbsp;The second is an NFC Medical ID chip that stores your medical and contact information, like found in the road <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/01/22/review-poc-ventral-air-spin-nfc-helmet-keeps-your-head-safe-health-data-at-hand/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ventral Air Spin NFC</a>. Should you be found unconscious or unable to communicate, the chip can provide rescuers access to this vital data.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet, top view\" width=\"800\" height=\"462\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-727x420.jpg 727w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-top-727x420.jpg 727w\"></a></p><p>The Kortal’s shell offers plenty of ventilation (the vent layout is similar to the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/12/10/review-pocs-tectal-race-spin-helmet-crave-sunglasses-and-joint-vpd-air-knee-pads/\">Tectal Race SPIN</a>, which I found very effective), and they even made sure your goggle strap won’t cover any of the vents. Furthermore, the rear vents also act as an ‘Eye Garage’ sunglass carrier.</p><p>Over the Kortal’s EPS liner is a unibody polycarbonate shell featuring Aramid Bridge construction underneath for extra strength. The deep shell design offers optimal skull coverage, dropping low at the temples and across the back of the head. &nbsp;POC keeps their strap system simple, with Y-shaped adjusters that spread the straps widely around your ears and a buckle closure at the chin.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal Race MIPS helmet, side\" width=\"800\" height=\"637\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-297x236.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-768x612.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-696x554.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-527x420.jpg 527w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-297x236.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-768x612.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-696x554.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-Race-MIPS-side-527x420.jpg 527w\"></a></p><p>The Kortal Race MIPS features POC’s patented break-away visor to help reduce neck injury in a crash. &nbsp;The visor provides four positions, and leaves ample room for goggles when fully lifted up. On that note, this helmet was designed to fit seamlessly with POC’s Ora goggles (or those Devour sunglasses).</p><p>Assisted riders will be stoked to know the Kortal Race MIPS doesn’t just meet the usual MTB safety standards, it’s actually certitifed for eMTBs traveling at higher speeds too (meeting the Dutch NTA 8776 standard).</p><p>Claimed weights for the Kortal Race MIPS are 390g for XS/S, 390g for M/L, and 470g for XL/XXL. Retail price for the top-spec Kortal Race MIPS&nbsp; is $250 / 250€, and five different colorways are available.</p><h3>POC Kortal mountain bike helmet, stripped back to the protection essentials</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink.jpg\" alt=\"POC Kortal helmet, pink\" width=\"800\" height=\"671\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-297x249.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-768x644.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-696x584.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-501x420.jpg 501w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-297x249.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-768x644.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-696x584.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Kortal-pink-501x420.jpg 501w\"></a></p><p>The Kortal helmet bears the same overall design as the Race MIPS version, but does not build in the Multi-directional Impact Protection System, RECCO reflector, or NFC Medical ID chip. The base Kortal does retain POC’s breakaway visor, and is also certified for eMTB use.</p><p>Claimed weighs for the Kortal come in a bit lighter than the Race MIPS version, at 360g for XS/S, 380g for M/L, and 440g for XL/XXL. The basic&nbsp; Kortal sells for $200 / 200€, and is available in eight color schemes.</p><h3>Devour Clarity sunglasses:</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle.jpg\" alt=\"POC Devour Clarity sunglasses, angle\" width=\"800\" height=\"479\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-768x460.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-696x417.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-701x420.jpg 701w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-768x460.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-696x417.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-angle-701x420.jpg 701w\"></a></p><p>Designed to be an almost-goggle, the Devour Clarity sunglasses boast huge lenses to offer maximum eye protection and an undisturbed field-of-view. Even their lean frames were designed to not interrupt your peripheral vision.</p><p>Not limited to one style of riding, the Devour sunglasses feature POC’s Clarity lenses, color-tuned to enhance definition on either road or trail. The lenses also provide complete UV400 protection, come with an anti-scratch coating, and are coated with Ri-Pel to fend off dirt, oil, sweat, salt, dust &amp; water.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side.jpg\" alt=\"POC Devour Clarity sunglasses, side\" width=\"800\" height=\"424\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-297x157.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-768x407.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-696x369.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-792x420.jpg 792w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-297x157.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-768x407.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-696x369.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-side-792x420.jpg 792w\"></a></p><p>One clever feature of the Devours is their adjustability. The length and grip of the Devour’s temples can be adjusted, as can their soft, grippy rubber nose piece. This should allow a wide range of riders to achieve a comfortable, secure fit.</p><figure id=\"attachment_252162\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252162\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside.jpg\" alt=\"POC Devour Clarity sunglasses, inside\" width=\"800\" height=\"466\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-768x447.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-696x405.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-721x420.jpg 721w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-768x447.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-696x405.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/POC-Devour-Clarity-sunglasses-inside-721x420.jpg 721w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252162\">*Images c. POC Sports</figcaption></figure><p>The Devour Clarity’s frames encourage airflow to keep fogging at bay, and the lenses are easily interchangeable. &nbsp;The Devours come in seven frame colors with either a Brown Mirror or Grey Deep Green Mirror lens. Each pair includes an extra clear lens and a soft pouch/lens cloth. Their retail price is $250 / 250€… yes, the same price as the top-tier Kortal Race MIPS helmet</p><p>The Kortal Race MIPS, Kortal, and Devour Clarity sunglasses are all now available online and in stores.</p><p><a href=\"https://pocsports.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>POCsports.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Steve Fisher","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8c3f34c2be9583316035f26d036e8cab619cc5c084468bd22a2b448808663b19","category":"Cycling"}